To configure with minimum settings without setting hostname or IP etc.
ovftool --acceptAllEulas --datastore="nfs-ubuntu-01" --name="esxi7-01" --net:"VM Network"="VM 1525" ./Nested_ESXi7.0_Appliance_Template_v1.ova vi://vcsa.tpmlab.vmware.com/Datacenter/host/Nested-PKS

To figure out what additional property settings can be configured
ovftool ./Nested_ESXi7.0_Appliance_Template_v1.ova

